 * Available variables:
 * - site_wrapper_element - default "div"
 * - site_wrapper_class_names - for an extra class - default: classname is the name of the region
 * - site_content_prefix
 * - site_content_suffix
 *
 * Available block:
 * - site_content
 *
 * see:
 * 03-organisms/site/_site.twig
